text:
League 1
ASSE - Monaco: the canvas ignites for the victory of the Greens!
ASSE won at home against Monaco 1-0 thanks to a goal from Denis Bouanga. Discover the best reactions of the canvas after this success Etienne.
03 Nov 2019, 22:00 by Antoine Chirat
After a sluggish first half, the Greens finally raised the lead in the second half to win against AS Monaco thanks to a goal from Denis Bouanga. Thanks to this success, the Greens return in the first half of the championship and are now 8th, just ahead of Olympique Lyonnais and Brest. Discover the best reactions following this meeting.
